spec_data.Name: gcc-offload-nvptx
spec_data.License: GPLv3+ and GPLv3+ with exceptions and GPLv2+ with exceptions and LGPLv2+ and BSD
spec_data.Description:
The gcc-offload-nvptx package provides offloading support for
NVidia PTX.  OpenMP and OpenACC programs linked with -fopenmp will
by default add PTX code into the binaries, which can be offloaded
to NVidia PTX capable devices if available.
